<p class="c8"><span class="c14">Sadly, it&rsquo;s time for you to leave this site. &nbsp;Now that you know the origin of the only magic used in this ritual, it might be possible to glean a little more information from it, but you&rsquo;re going to have to leave that to your team; you&rsquo;ve been away from Eschaton too long as it is, and you&rsquo;ll be pleasantly surprised if your office hasn&rsquo;t been firebombed by the time you get back. &nbsp;Or if the Learned Hall hasn&rsquo;t caught fire. &nbsp;Or the Auditorium. &nbsp;You&rsquo;d be pretty okay if the Philosopher&rsquo;s Bistro caught fire. &nbsp;That place has needed renovation for nearly a hundred years now.</span></p> 
