<p class="c8"><span class="c19">You are </span><span class="c56 c32">Slabal</span><span class="c19">, and, although you have long held the title of &nbsp;Layer of the Path, in practice, most of the time your duties required you to repair, maintain, or, at the most extreme, </span><span class="c19 c11">re</span><span class="c14">-lay a path.</span></p> 
