<p class="c9"><span class="c39 c19">&ldquo;A task well completed. &nbsp;The main way is complete, for now. &nbsp;It will require final inspection, but all preliminary inspection indicates that it is of the finest craftelfship. &nbsp;Karlos, you are to be commended with full emphasis for the diligence of you and your laborers. &nbsp;Entrep, your work in accurately levelling the way&rsquo;s foundation is also to be praised. &nbsp;Congratulations to all.&rdquo;</span></p> 
<p class="c9 c30"><span class="c39 c19"></span></p> 
<p class="c8"><span class="c14">Eyes brighten. &nbsp;In a few cases, smiles even sprout. &nbsp;It is, perhaps, overly exuberant, but you can understand their passion. &nbsp;This was a major undertaking, and a vital one.</span></p> 
