<p class="c9"><span class="c39 c19">&ldquo;I believe it would serve to commemorate this work by concluding this work day early. &nbsp;An additional shift of recreation and repast to you all. &nbsp;Entrep, if you would attend, I wish to speak with you before you go to join them.&rdquo;</span></p> 
<p class="c9 c30"><span class="c39 c19"></span></p> 
<p class="c8"><span class="c14">At your words, the assembled Crag, both laborers and craftselves alike, fan out to the other parts of Eparchy. &nbsp;Within the bunks and halls already previously erected, you suspect that soon cookfires will ignite and conversation will rise. &nbsp;One of their number, Entrep, remains as requested. &nbsp;Her wizened features belay her age; by no means even close to as aged as the Esteemed, she still shows those subtle marks of seniority that all Onagi hope to one day cultivate. &nbsp;They are marks of wisdom. &nbsp;Marks of experience.</span></p> 
<p class="c1"><span class="c14"></span></p> 
<p class="c8"><span class="c23 c19">&ldquo;A path well laid, Layer. &nbsp;Heh. &nbsp;It always sounds odd, to repeat myself like that. &nbsp;Jocularity aside, I assume there are other tasks which now require our attention?&rdquo;</span></p> 
